{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与乌卓密谋逃亡计划，命乌卓率众人经地道撤退至齐国边境，自己留下断后。雅夫人含泪同意离去，信陵君亲自送行并安排轻骑兵护送。项少龙借故留在府中，趁夜潜入平原夫人住所救出被软禁的赵倩，为她换上远行装备缚于背上。符毒放火制造混乱，项少龙携赵倩经少原君房中地道逃出信陵君府。黑夜中在大梁街头遭嚣魏牟率十九名高手伏击，项少龙以木剑和飞虹剑拼死搏斗，连杀四人重创三人，包括杀死高手宁充，但自己也身负重伤。危急时刻，纪嫣然戴面具策马持弩弓长矛杀到，以漫天矛影迫退嚣魏牟，救出二人落荒而逃。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们已依你吩咐，在营地下打了一条地道通到营后一座山林里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "又派人由地道穿过去，赶造十多艘木筏，密藏在一条接连大沟小河旁的丛林中，顺水而去，两天可抵达齐国南面边境。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "雅夫人她们今天黄昏前会回到营地去，你教成胥装模作样，坚持明天才上路，那信陵君便不会提防我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那你如何混出城来呢？信陵君定会使人把你看紧。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "我绝不能离开，否则谁也逃不掉。要凭那条地道把人撤走，最少要一个时辰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "太阳下山你们便须立即行动，弄些假人以掩人耳目，所有战甲、马匹和重型装备都要留下来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "抵齐境后再设法由牧民处买些马匹，昼伏夜行，定可安然回到赵国去，总之秘诀在'隐秘'两个字，你当自己是马贼就行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那孙姑爷怎么办？我丢下你回去，主人定会要了我的命！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "至少我也要留下来陪你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "这是命令，你定要照我的话去做，没有了你，成胥定成不了事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "我绝不会不爱惜自己生命的，而且还有周详的计划，不但足可自救，还可带走赵倩。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孙姑爷若三个月内回不到赵国去，我乌卓便刎颈自尽，以报答孙姑爷比天还高的情义。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没有你，雅儿怎也不走！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！我特别调来一营轻骑兵，明天清早护送他们回去好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "由现在开始，少龙最好留在府里，一来养足精神，免得节外生枝，坏了大事，我已派人把赵倩送往隐秘处藏好，好使少龙心无旁骛，应付明天的宴会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "纪嫣然今早找你干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "我也不知她找我做什么，东南西北扯着我说了一会儿后便走了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "今晚我想独自一人练剑，最好不要派人来伺候我。嘿！没有雅夫人，那些婢女又那么动人，我怕一时忍不住就糟了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！抱我入房！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人！不是要迟些才可以吗？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家要现在嘛！还不抱我进去？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "下人",
      "listener": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人，君上有急事请你立即去见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_yuan_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平原夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "小宝贝听话吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙，今天看你还能逃到哪里去？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "早想到你会临阵退缩，所以日夜不停监视着你，哈！你背上就是那美丽的公主吧！今晚我保证可令她快乐地死去。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老子享受过后，你们人人有份！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "倩儿！这是生死关头，你定要提起勇气，怎也要躲在我背后。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "倩儿跟紧我！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "倩儿跟我走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还不上马！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    }
  ],
